 href=\"http://wiki.joyme.com/blhx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwiki.joyme.com%2Fblhx%2F&d=yxrIo4T3sg0dtfJjKHS33dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=e655e28b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://wiki.joyme.com/blhx/</a><br />\n<br />\n巴哈新手教學:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=32550&amp;snA=57&amp;tnum=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D32550%26snA%3D57%26tnum%3D2&d=yxrIo4T3sg0dtfJjKHS33dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=090a6934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=32550&amp;snA=57&amp;tnum=2</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=32550&amp;snA=81&amp;tnum=7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D32550%26snA%3D81%26tnum%3D7&d=yxrIo4T3sg0dtfJjKHS33dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2488908e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=32550&amp;snA=81&amp;tnum=7</a><br />\n<br />\n裝備推介:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/230523_9a11768d2c2eea7c331011b06a7d4eb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F230523_9a11768d2c2eea7c331011b06a7d4eb2.png&h=361a0453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n艦娘排行:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/230546_9675c1ff34145d7b1a68d3ddb6c0e555.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F230546_9675c1ff34145d7b1a68d3ddb6c0e555.png&h=8d21f961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時無咩用嘅連登提督表，想搵巴打做Fd子無咁寂寞嘅可以填下<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1qf6E-KdtRy6g8Qib7FVxPrUt5PMTvWBCC-zEa9-ocBM/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1qf6E-KdtRy6g8Qib7FVxPrUt5PMTvWBCC-zEa9-ocBM%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=yxrIo4T3sg0dtfJjKHS33dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c98a6002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1qf6E-KdtRy6g8Qib7FVxPrUt5PMTvWBCC-zEa9-ocBM/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A:<br />\n<br />\nQ:洗唔洗首抽?<br />\nA:基本上唔洗,藍皮同紫皮艦都好勁(請看上圖)<br />\n<br />\nQ:大家玩咩SER?<br />\nA:個個SER都有連登仔係到,但係大家自己集中係ルルイエ、舞鶴<br />\n<br />\nQ:入唔到我地個SER點算?<br />\nA:建議照玩,因為隻GAME唔算多互動性,就算同一個SER都係自己玩自己<br />\n<br />\nQ:幾時突破好?<br />\nA:建議盡量升爆左隻艦先.因為突破左之後會十分食油<br />\n<br />\nQ:唔夠打下一個圖阿 點算?<br />\nA:你要有足夠既肝力,肝爆上一個圖 直到可以打下一個圖[/quote]<br />\n<br />\nQ:限pool嘅艦會唔會出係普通pool?<br />\nA:會,不過唔知幾時會有,等唔到就課啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提提大家：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">藏王重工10金箱賭局</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1抽胡德？5抽翔鶴？十抽五航+企業？你唔係以為咁樣就叫歐掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩哩隻驚要驗血睇下自己係歐洲人定非洲人又點會靠賭艦哩啲7%SSR嘅街貨野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係想知自己咩血統嘅話，當然係開<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">明石油嘅</span></span>金箱睇下中幾多隻金吊臂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56a44fcbd6f7a15a1835e8550213ec5a335de3c","tid":472930,"uid":23718,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/205748_4605395a415896870be3aff99afbfd24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F205748_4605395a415896870be3aff99afbfd24.jpg&h=bd92a782&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f8b2e8865a64cb6d08c3ab30b6c89d39024cbb4","tid":472930,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:37:57.000Z","msg":"嘩咩事，突然棄晒game?"},{"pid":"8fd4ba57fd5da1648e737202754ffc19f6c5080d","tid":472930,"uid":79872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩咩事，突然棄晒game?</blockquote><br />